    "To address this, we design and apply a procedure to evaluate predictions made specifically on computationally-predicted structures of various accuracies; this reveals that IF-SitePred is more robust to low-accuracy structures and is able to better exploit the information contained in multiple structures of the same protein.Fig. 33Fig.",
